  </knowledge>
  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read alerts.bicep (from task 004) to understand existing structure.</step>
    <step order="2">Author scheduledQueryRule resource targeting App Insights component. Query as specified above; threshold: any env with last_success > 100 days; severity: 2; window: 1 day.</step>
    <step order="3">Add `appInsightsResourceId` param if not present (action group + AI resource ID).</step>
    <step order="4">`az bicep build` validates.</step>
    <step order="5">Update TASK-INDEX 🔲 → ✅.</step>
  </steps>
